<section class="about" id="about">
    <div class="about-content">
      <p>Our approach combines strategic thinking, clean design, and the latest technologies to create solutions that are both beautiful and functional. Each project is crafted with attention to detail and a focus on user experience.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <style>
    .about {
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .about-content p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .about {
        padding: 2rem 1rem;
      }
      
      .about-content p {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
    }
  </style>